  "texts": [
    "Specifically, P16 explained it as \"I felt really engaged because the drag and drop was asking me to do some stuff\".",
    "In addition, a high level of engagement also resulted from being prompted to think through the question.",
    "As P18 explained, \"because it makes me kind of think through the solution rather than just copy and paste it. \"",
    "Furthermore, P7 reported, \"I could visualize where all the different parts of the problem are going to go, and it made me think more about the problem. \"",
    "Conversely, participants reported feeling disengaged when using the baseline support of just receiving an AI-generated solution."
  ],
